rating_comment: The place was good. Only there was no option for any sunlight to enter home. And the mobile data and wifi was not good. Other than that, the host was communicative and helpful. The location is good and safe.

rating_comment: The place is huge and I really enjoyed it. It is well equipped and the host does everything to make the stay pleasant.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · February 2024,  · Stayed with kids
rating_comment:
Our stay at Kainath’s place in Dhaka was wonderful. Kainath was accommodating with our early check-in and late checkout, which was especially helpful as we were traveling with a toddler. The place is spacious, clean, and secure, with access to local stores and food delivery services like foodpanda.
Kainath’s flexibility with our check-in and checkout times was greatly appreciated, making our stay more manageable with a toddler in tow. The spacious and clean accommodation exceeded our expectations, providing a comfortable and relaxing environment.
The security measures in place at Kainath’s place gave us peace of mind, allowing us to fully enjoy our time in Dhaka. The convenient location near local shopping stores and food delivery services added to the overall convenience and enjoyment of our stay.
Great peaceful and quiet location. Neat and clean. I would love to go back again.

Rating, 5 stars,  · January 2024,  · Stayed with kids
rating_comment: This place was amazing as I expected. Everything was very organized & clean. The location is pretty convenient & it’s in the center of the city. The airport is 15-20 minutes drive from the location.
Host and manager both are amazing person and helpful. And the best place I have ever visited so much clean and friendly hope to visits again. Thank you 😊

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · January 2024,  · Stayed with kids
rating_comment:
This is a great house to stay with family. We enjoyed the spacious living room to gossip with our family members. Kitchen is another cool area of this house. A lot of appliances were ready to use.
Will come back again!

The house was very clean and had all the amenities you can think of, also the host was very supportive and was always easy to reach out. This property is highly recommended and I will definitely revisit this property in future.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · December 2023,  · Stayed over a week
rating_comment:
Kainath's apartment was probably one of the best we have stayed in outside Europe and North America. A very well maintained apartment, spotlessly clean and very tastefully and functionally furnished. Kainath and her Mum were always in touch to provide immediate help and support whenever we needed them.
We look forward to staying at her apartment again.
Thank you Kainath and your Mum. You two have been a great host.
